                     <interp inst="t18250217-13-off78" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250217-13-cd79" type="crimeDate">28th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250217-13-off78 t18250217-13-cd79"></join>, a bag, value 6 d., and 28 lbs. of coffee, value 40 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18250217-13-victim148" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Travers
               <interp inst="t18250217-13-victim148" type="surname" value="Travers"></interp>
